quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  29,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  29,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  29,2,kiya log yeh khayaal kiye hue hain ke sirf yeh kehnay se ke hum imaan le aeye chore diye jayen ge aur unn ki azmaish nahi ki jaye gi
  29,3,aur jo log unn se pehlay ho chuke hain hum ne unn ko bhi aazmaaya tha ( aur un ko bhi aazmayin ge ) so khuda unn ko zaroor maloom karen ge jo ( apne imaan mein ) sachey hain aur unn ko bhi jo jhutay hain
  29,4,kiya woh log jo buray kaam karte hain yeh samjhay hue hain ke yeh hamaray qaboo se nikal jayen ge. jo khayaal yeh karte hain bura hai
  29,5,jo shakhs khuda ki mulaqaat ki umeed rakhta ho khuda ka ( muqarrarkiya howa ) waqt zaroor anay wala hai. aur woh suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai
  29,6,aur jo shakhs mehnat karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye mehnat karta hai. aur khuda to saaray Jahan se be parwa hai
  29,7,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay hum un ke gunaaho ko unn se daur kar dein ge aur un ko un ke aamaal ka bohat acha badla den ge
  29,8,aur hum ne ensaan ko apne maa baap ke sath naik sulooq karne ka hukum diya hai. ( ae mukhatib ) agar tairay maa baap tairay darpay hon ke to mere sath kisi ko shareek banaye jis ki haqeeqat ki tujhe waqfiyat nahi. to un ka kehna nah mannio. tum ( sab ) ko meri taraf lout kar aana hai. phir jo kuch tum karte they mein tum ko jta dun ga
  29,9,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ko hum naik logon mein daakhil karen ge
  29,10,aur baaz log aisay hain jo kehte hain ke hum khuda par imaan laaye jab unn ko khuda ( ke raste ) mein koi aeza pahunchti hai to logon ki aeza ko ( yun ) samajte hain jaisay khuda ka azaab. agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se madad puhanche to kehte hain ke hum tumahray sath they.kiya jo ahal aalam ke seenon mein hai khuda is se waaqif nahi ?
  29,11,aur khuda unn ko zaroor maloom kere ga jo ( sachey ) momin hain aur mnafqon ko bhi maloom karkay rahay ga
  29,12,aur jo kafir hain woh mominoun se kehte hain ke hamaray tareeq ki pairwi karo hum tumahray gunah athaliN ge. halaank woh unn ke gunaaho ka kuch bhi boojh aُthane walay nahi. kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
  29,13,aur yeh apne boojh bhi uthain ge aur apne bojhon ke sath aur ( logon ke ) boojh bhi. aur jo bohtan yeh bandhte rahay qayamat ke din unn ki unn se zaroor prssh hogi
  29,14,aur hum ne Nooh ko unn ki qoum ki taraf bheja to woh un mein pachaas baras kam hazaar baras rahay phir unn ko tufaan ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha. aur woh zalim they
  29,15,phir hum ne Nooh ko aur kashti walon ko nijaat di aur kashti ko ahal aalam ke liye nishani bana diya
  29,16,aur ibrahim ko ( yaad karo ) jab onhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke khuda ki ibadat karo aur is se daro agar tum samajh rakhtay ho to yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai
  29,17,to tum khuda ko chore kar buton ko pujte aur tufaan bandhte ho to jin logon ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho woh tum ko rizaq dainay ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay pas khuda hi ke haan se rizaq talab karo aur isi ki ibadat karo aur isi ka shukar karo isi ki taraf tum lout kar jao ge
  29,18,aur agar tum ( meri ) takzieeb karo to tum se pehlay bhi ummatain ( apne payghambaroon ki ) takzieeb krchki hain. aur paighambar ke zimmay khol kar suna dainay ke siwa aur kuch nahi
  29,19,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda kis terhan khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta phir ( kis terhan ) is ko baar baar peda karta rehta hai. yeh khuda ko aasaan hai
  29,20,keh do ke malik mein chalo phiro aur dekho ke is ne kis terhan khalqat ko pehli dafaa pedakiya hai phir khuda hi pichli paidaiesh peda kere ga. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  29,21,woh jisay chahay azaab day aur jis par chahay reham kere. aur usi ki taraf tum lout’tay jao ge
  29,22,aur tum ( uss ko ) nah zameen mein aajiz kar saktay ho nah aasman mein aur nah khuda ke siwa tumhara koi dost hai aur nah madadgaar
  29,23,aur jin logon ne khuda ki aayton se aur is ke milnay se inkaarkiya woh meri rehmat se na umeed hogaye hain aur un ko dard dainay wala azaab hoga
  29,24,to unn ki qoum ke log jawab mein bolay to yeh bolay ke ussay maar daalo ya jala do. magar khuda ne unn ko aag ( ki soozish ) se bchalya. jo log imaan rakhtay hain unn ke liye is mein nishanain hain
  29,25,aur ibrahim ne kaha ke tum jo khuda ko chore kar buton ko le baithy ho to duniya ki zindagi mein baahum dosti ke liye ( magar ) phir qayamat ke din tum aik dosray ( ki dosti ) se inkaar kar do ge aur aik dosray par laanat bhaijho ge aur tumhara thikana dozakh hoga aur koi tumhara madadgaar nah hoga
  29,26,pas unn par ( aik ) Loot imaan laaye aur ( ibrahim ) kehnay lagey ke mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf hijrat karne wala hon. bay shak woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  29,27,aur hum ne unn ko ashq aur Yaqoob bakhshay aur unn ki aulaad mein paigambri aur kitaab ( muqarrar ) kar di aur un ko duniya mein bhi unn ka sila inayatkiya aur woh akhirat mein bhi naik logon mein hon ge
  29,28,aur Loot ( ko yaad karo ) jab onhon ne apni qoum se kaha ke tum ( ajab ) be hiyai ke murtakib hotay ho. tum se pehlay ahal aalam mein se kisi ne aisa kaam nahikiya
  29,29,tum kyun ( lazzat ke iraday se ) london ki taraf ma-il hotay aur ( musafiron ki ) rehzani karte ho aur apni mjlson mein napasandeedah kaam karte ho. to unn ki qoum ke log jawab mein bolay to yeh bolay ke agar tum sachey ho to hum par azaab le aao
  29,30,Loot ne kaha ke ae mere perwar-digaar un mufsid logon ke muqablay mein mujhe nusrat inayat farma
  29,31,aur jab hamaray farishtay ibrahim ke paas khusi ki khabar le kar aeye to kehnay lagey ke hum is bastii ke logon ko halaak kar dainay walay hain ke yahan ke rehne walay nafarman hain
  29,32,ibrahim ne kaha ke is mein to Loot bhi hain. woh kehnay lagey ke jo log yahan ( rehtay ) hain hamein sab maloom hain. hum unn ko aur unn ke ghar walon ko bchalin ge bajuz unn ki biwi ke woh peechay rehne walon mein hogi
  29,33,aur jab hamaray farishtay Loot ke paas aeye to woh unn ( ki wajah ) se nakhush aur tang dil hue. firshton ne kaha kuch khauf nah kijiyej. aur nah ranj kijiyej hum aap ko aur aap ke ghar walon ko bchalin ge magar aap ki biwi ke peechay rehne walon mein hogi
  29,34,hum is bastii ke rehne walon par is sabab se ke yeh bud-kardari karte rahay hain aasman se azaab nazil karne walay hain
  29,35,aur hum ne samajhney walay logon ke liye is bastii se aik khuli nishani chore di
  29,36,aur Mudin ki taraf unn ke bhai Shoiab ko ( bheja ) to onhon ne kaha ( ae qoum ) khuda ki ibadat karo aur pichlle din ke anay ki umeed rakho aur malik mein fasaad nah مچاؤ
  29,37,magar onhon ne unn ko jhoota samgha so unn ko zalzalay ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay
  29,38,aur Aad aur smod ko bhi ( hum ne halaak kar diya ) chunancha unn ke ( weraan ghar ) tumhari aankhon ke samnay hain aur shetan ne unn ke aamaal un ko aaraasta kar dukhaay aur un ko ( seedhay ) raste se rok diya. halaank woh dekhnay walay ( log ) they
  29,39,aur qaroon aur firaon aur Haman ko bhi ( halaak kar diya ) aur unn ke paas moose khuli nishani le kar aeye to woh malik mein maghrour hogaye aur hamaray qaboo se nikal jaane walay nah they
  29,40,to hum ne sab ko unn ke gunaaho ke sabab pakar liya. so un mein kuch to aisay they jin par hum ne patharon kameinhہ barsaya. aur kuch aisay they jin ko chngharh ne aapkrha aur kuch aisay they jin ko hum ne zameen mein dhansa diya. aur kuch aisay they jin ko ghark kar diya aur khuda aisa nah tha ke unn par zulm karta lekin wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
  29,41,jin logon ne khuda ke siwa ( ouron ko ) karsaaz bana rakha hai unn ki misaal makri ki si hai ke woh bhi aik ( terhan ka ) ghar banati hai. aur kuch shak nahi ke tamam gharon se kamzor makri ka ghar hai kash yeh ( is baat ko ) jantay
  29,42,yeh jis cheez ko khuda ke siwa pkarte hain ( khuwa ) woh kuch hi ho khuda ussay jaanta hai. aur woh ghalib aur hikmat wala hai
  29,43,aur yeh misalein hum logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye bayan karte hain aur ussay to ehley Danish hi samajte hain
  29,44,khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko hikmat ke sath pedakiya hai. kuch shak nahi ke imaan walon ke liye is mein nishani hai
  29,45,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! yeh ) kitaab jo tumhari taraf wahi ki gayi hai is ko parha karo aur namaz ke paband raho. kuch shak nahi ke namaz be hiyai aur buri baton se rokti hai. aur khuda ka zikar bara ( acha kaam ) hai. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda ussay jaanta hai
  29,46,aur ehley kitaab se jhagra nah karo magar aisay tareeq se ke nihayat acha ho. haan jo unn mein se be insafi karen ( unn ke sath isi terhan majadla karo ) aur keh do ke jo ( kitaab ) hum par utreen aur jo ( kitaaben ) tum par Utrain hum sab par imaan rakhtay hain aur hamara aur tumhara mabood aik hi hai aur hum usi ke farmanbardar hain
  29,47,aur isi terhan hum ne tumhari taraf kitaab aُtari hai. to jin logon ko hum ne kitaaben di theen woh is par imaan le atay hain. aur baaz un ( mushriq ) logon mein se bhi is par imaan le atay hain. aur hamari aayton se wohi inkaar karte hain jo kafir ( Azli ) hain
  29,48,aur tum is se pehlay koi kitaab nahi parhte they aur nah ussay apne haath se likh hi satke they aisa hota to ehley baatil zaroor shak karte
  29,49,balkay yeh roshan ayatain hain. jin logon ko ilm diya gaya hai unn ke seenon mein ( mehfooz ) aur hamari aayton se wohi log inkaar karte hain jo be insaaf hain
  29,50,aur ( kafir ) kehte hain ke is par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishanain kyun nazil nahi huien keh do ke nishanain to khuda hi ke paas hain. aur mein to khullam khula hadaayat karne wala hon
  29,51,kiya unn logon ke liye yeh kaafi nahi ke hum ne tum par kitaab nazil ki jo unn ko parh kar sunai jati hai. kuch shak nahi ke momin logon ke liye is mein rehmat aur nasiyaat hai
  29,52,keh do ke mere aur tumahray darmain khuda hi gawah kaafi hai jo cheez asmano mein aur zameen mein hai woh sab ko jaanta hai. aur jin logon ne baatil ko maana aur khuda se inkaarkiya wohi nuqsaan aُthane walay hain
  29,53,aur yeh log tum se azaab ke liye jaldi kar rahay hain. agar aik waqt muqarrar nah ( ho chuka ) hota to unn par azaab aabhi gaya hota. aur woh ( kisi waqt mein ) unn par zaroor nagahan aakar rahay ga aur unn ko maloom bhi nah hoga
  29,54,yeh tum se azaab ke liye jaldi kar rahay hain. aur dozakh to kafiroon ko ghair lainay wali hai
  29,55,jis din azaab unn ko unn ke ooper se aur neechay se dhaank le ga aur ( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke jo kaam tumkiya karte they ( ab ) unn ka maza chako
  29,56,ae mere Bandoo jo imaan laaye ho meri zameen farakh hai to meri hi ibadat karo
  29,57,har mutnaqas mout ka maza chakhnay wala hai. phir tum hamari hi taraf lout kar aao ge
  29,58,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay unn ko hum bahisht ke umche umche mehloon mein jagah den ge. jin ke neechay nehrain bah rahi hain. hamesha un mein rahen ge. ( naik ) amal karne walon ka ( yeh ) khoob badla hai
  29,59,jo sabr karte aur apne perwar-digaar par bharosa rakhtay hain
  29,60,aur bohat se janwar hain jo apna rizaq uthaiye nahi phirtay khuda hi un ko rizaq deta hai aur tum ko bhi. aur woh suneney wala aur jan-nay wala hai
  29,61,aur agar unn se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya. aur Sooraj aur chaand ko kis ne ( tumahray ) zair farmaankiya to keh den ge khuda ne. to phir yeh kahan ultay ja rahay hain
  29,62,khuda hi apne bundon mein se jis ke liye chahta hai rozi farakh kar deta hai aur jis ke liye chahta hai tang kar deta hai bay shak khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  29,63,aur agar tum un se pucho ke aasman se pani kis ne nazil farmaya phir is se zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad ( kis ne ) zindahkiya to keh den ge ke khuda ne. keh do ke khuda ka shukar hai. lekin un mein aksar nahi samajte
  29,64,aur yeh duniya ki zindagi to sirf khail aur tamasha hai aur ( hamesha ki ) zindagi ( ka maqam ) to akhirat ka ghar hai. kash yeh ( log ) samajte
  29,65,phir jab yeh kashti mein sawaar hotay hain to khuda ko pkarte ( aur ) khalis usi ki ibadat karte hain. lekin jab woh unn ko nijaat day kar khushki par pouncha deta hai to jhat shirk karne lagey jatay hain
  29,66,taakay jo hum ne unn ko bakhsha hai uss ki nashukri karen aur faida athayin ( so kher ) anqareeb unn ko maloom hojaye ga
  29,67,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne haram ko maqam aman banaya hai aur log is ke gird vnwah se uchak liye jatay hain.kiya yeh log baatil par aitqaad rakhtay hain aur khuda ki nematon ki nashukri karte hain
  29,68,aur is se zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhay ya jab haq baat uss ke paas aeye to is ki takzieeb kere.kiya kafiroon ka thikana jahannum mein nahi hai ?
  29,69,aur jin logon ne hamaray liye koshish ki hum unn ko zaroor apne raste dikha den ge. aur khuda to naiko karon ke sath hai
